  <lyrics>[V1]
 Ofrendasta apamunchej munakuywan, kusiywan,
 Kay himnoswan yupaychaspa Señor Jesusninchejman.
 
[V2]
 Semanapi ñawpaj p’unchay raqapuna Señorpai
 Apamusqanchejmanjina bendidwasunchej Pay.
 
